reviews.content: A quintessential “nhậu” restaurant that’s suitable for group gatherings. The food was okay but nothing memorable. Price was reasonable though.
The customer service experience is great. Food is 4/5. Tasty however; doesn’t leave much memorable note. “Mam tom-shrimp paste” is authentically from Thanh Hoa, quite nice. …
Good place for event birthday, weeding celebrations ... good foods.
Everything is better than what i expected...
Very good for family gatherings and small party reunion, good traditional vietnamese food and quite affordable if you choose good menu set
Lower satisfactory customer service. Just passable food. Narrow space. . But High price. Bye bye
My grandma's birthday , the food was ok , staff was ok , the park is ok either
Very hot but air condition not available for small groups of persons
